<subtitle>Program interface</subtitle>

<h2>Toolbar</h2>

<image>images/toolbar.jpg</image>

<li>Open document</li>Open document from disk
<li>Back</li>Return to previous document
<li>Forward</li>Move forward to next document in history
<li>Reload</li>Reload current document
<li>About</li>Show About dialog
<h2>Menu</h2>
<li>File</li>
<li2>~ Open        <sc>Ctrl-O</sc></li2> Open document
<li2>~ Reload      <sc>Ctrl-R</sc></li2> Reload current document
<li2>~ View source<sc>Ctrl-V</sc></li2>	 Show the source of current page
<li2>~ Settings<sc>Ctrl-S</sc></li2>     Activate settings dialog
<li2>~ Exit <sc>Ctrl-X</sc></li2>	 Exit from SML Viewer

<li>Go</li>
Open document using history
<li>Help</li>
<li2>~ Users' Guide<sc>F1</sc></li2> Show document help.sml
<li2>~ About program</li2>  Show document <path><link>readme.sml</link>readme.sml</path>
<li2>~ About <sc>Ctrl-F1</sc>  </li2> Display About dialog

<para>---------------------------------------------------------------------</para>
<subtitle>Settings</subtitle>

<li>Folder with style files</li>Select directory where are stored files with styles.
<li>Font</li>	You can select font which will be used for displaying documents.
<li>Background Color</li> Choose window background color.
<li>Display Priority</li>This parameter affects the speed of displaying document.
<para>Recommended value is Idle.</para>
